title: Hydrology: Bathymetry
name: Hydrology: Bathymetry
description: Data from transects of soundings showing the bathymetry of the Coos Bay. Data points are just several points along the transects of the entire bay.

properties.data restrictions: The information contained in the data files represent the results of surveys made on the dates indicated and can only be considered as indicating general conditions existing at that time.
properties.location(s): Transect along Coos Bay channel from entrance to Charleston Bridge then through Bunker Hill
properties.hydrographic region: Marine, Marine Dominated (31-20 psu); Mesohaline (28-15 psu)
